{"tid":403872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回收業界明起恢復收廢紙","createTime":"2017-09-17T14:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T18:19:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd68fdc1da0f350e183dbb9bf3f73cbaf2a8913","tid":403872,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170917/large/1505656025_0b68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170917%2Flarge%2F1505656025_0b68.jpg&h=4200c1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n部分回收商上周五起暫停收集和處理廢紙，本港多區紙皮堆積無法及時處理。發起停收廢紙的回收業界在晚上宣佈，明日開始將陸續恢復回收廢紙，因為政府已承諾協助回收商出口廢紙。<br />\n<br />\n環保廢料再造業總會會長劉耀成表示，已經通知總會屬下會員明天起陸續恢復收廢紙，預料星期二可以全面恢復收廢紙，又指業界近日的行動，為前線清潔人員及基層市民帶來困擾，感到抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n不過劉預計，若中國兩間造紙廠最終未能獲得批文，業界將轉為開拓東南亞市場，無法吸納全港廢紙，預計至10月底倉庫就會爆滿，屆時無法再收廢紙，最終亦只能把廢紙送到堆填區。"},{"pid":"6680b6bce0e81451669fff657e076a23d33f0b93","tid":403872,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2314040a2ef91be4f4c3f475758ed45a732da71","tid":403872,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"老友記齊發揮獅子山通宵精神，快啲落街耕田啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b7551e10d9a3e44ef3f9963fd595858c0fd05c","tid":403872,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"環保變成商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cd4ea308357287dd571a873cf0edfe03f63a6c","tid":403872,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"好似乞丐咁乞中國放入口。真係賤業"},{"pid":"11b2869d6f9d31580693cc69f938c8a919251668","tid":403872,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保變成商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小學雞？環保商業左幾十世啦"},{"pid":"8b9ab22126d5cb51de9713818a7ec6d976fd1b05","tid":403872,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話停收7日<br />\n冇d骨氣</blockquote><br />\n找到好價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先停收，再低價收阿婆存貨<br />\n夠貨，又可以高價賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1854be61bd0327d0585278134dfe6306682e5cd4","tid":403872,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"多謝納稅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54e37f78008e6e21b0a20d8b0544fa8eedcf5bb","tid":403872,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e52c49cebbdc9b8b39ce87edbcddd91fdadd6bfa","tid":403872,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb68988e7eba78193fdb006e60f5e64aa5702dac","tid":403872,"uid":37853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"仲好<br />\n運曬過去東南亞國家<br />\n大陸食唔到條水又少咁 d gdp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2b44489561bb514a4a2c7116c839d1aa8432f3","tid":403872,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T18:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b66fbebec725d69ec105d03f69a4755b17a6a8","tid":403872,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}